# Raw benchmark result TOMLs carry full per-run solution vectors and are huge
# (100s of MB per large-band file). Only the slim summaries + index.json are
# version-controlled and served by the viewer; regenerate slims locally with
# `python3 docs/benchmarks/render.py`.
docs/benchmarks/data/**/*.toml
!docs/benchmarks/data/**/*.slim.toml
